<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>YourWriteBuddy | Free Writing Tools</title><meta name="description" content="Free writing tools including Word Counter, Character Counter, Reading Time Calculator and more."><style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f8fafc;
    color:#222;
}

header{
    background:white;
    box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    padding:20px;
}

nav{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:bold;
    color:#2563eb;
}

.hero{
    text-align:center;
    padding:80px 20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
    color:#666;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.tools{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:40px 20px 80px;
}

.tools h2{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:14px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-5px);
}

.card h3{
    color:#2563eb;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card p{
    color:#666;
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    background:white;
    color:#777;
    border-top:1px solid #eee;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
    font-size:2.2rem;
}

}
</style></head>
<body><header>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">✍️ YourWriteBuddy</div>
    </nav>
</header><section class="hero"><h1>Free Writing Tools for Everyone</h1>

<p>
    Count words, analyze text, estimate reading time,
    and improve your writing with simple and free online tools.
</p>

</section><section class="tools"><h2>Popular Tools</h2>

<div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Word Counter</h3>
        <p>Count words, characters, sentences and paragraphs instantly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Character Counter</h3>
        <p>Track characters for essays, posts and social media.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Reading Time Calculator</h3>
        <p>Estimate how long content takes to read.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Speech Time Calculator</h3>
        <p>Prepare speeches and presentations confidently.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Case Converter</h3>
        <p>Convert text to uppercase, lowercase and title case.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>Grammar Checker</h3>
        <p>Check and improve grammar with ease.</p>
    </div>

</div>

</section><footer>
    © 2026 YourWriteBuddy • Free Writing Tools
</footer></body>
</html>
